19#ifndef CANONICALIZE_H_
20# define CANONICALIZE_H_
21
22enum canonicalize_mode_t
23 {
24 /* All components must exist. */
25 CAN_EXISTING = 0,
26
27 /* All components excluding last one must exist. */
28 CAN_ALL_BUT_LAST = 1,
29
30 /* No requirements on components existence. */
31 CAN_MISSING = 2
32 };
33typedef enum canonicalize_mode_t canonicalize_mode_t;
34
35char *canonicalize_filename_mode (const char *, canonicalize_mode_t);
36
37# if !HAVE_CANONICALIZE_FILE_NAME
38char *canonicalize_file_name (const char *);
39# endif
40
41#endif /* !CANONICALIZE_H_ */
